tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE trading_algorithms (
    algorithm_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_name VARCHAR NOT NULL,
    parameter_set JSONB NOT NULL,
    historical_data JSONB NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE backtest_results (
    backtest_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    algorithm_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    parameters JSONB NOT NULL,
    result DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
    backtest_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE historical_data (
    data_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    symbol VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL,
    date DATE NOT NULL,
    open_price DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
    high_price DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
    low_price DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
    close_price DECIMAL(10,2) NOT NULL,
    volume INTEGER NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE historical_data (
	history_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	stock_symbol VARCHAR(10) NOT NULL,
	date DATE NOT NULL,
	high_price DECIMAL NOT NULL,
	low_price DECIMAL NOT NULL,
	open_price DECIMAL NOT NULL,
	close_price DECIMAL NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE backtesting_results (
	result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
	algorithm_id INT NOT NULL,
	history_id INT NOT NULL,
	profit DECIMAL NOT NULL,
	evaluation_date DATE NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE HistoricalMarketData (
    data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    open_price DECIMAL,
    close_price DECIMAL,
    high_price DECIMAL,
    low_price DECIMAL
);
